OL,3,CMan caught drink driving with child in
OL,4,Cthe car in Barnsley appears at court
OL,6,FA driver who was caught drink driving
OL,7,Fwith a child in the car in Barnsley
OL,8,Fhas appeared before court.
OL,10,FEarlier this year, on 29 May, a roads
OL,11,Fpolicing officer on patrol sighted a
OL,12,Fsilver Citroen Dispatch swerving
OL,13,Facross the road in Goldthorpe.
OL,15,FSuspecting the driver was under the
OL,16,Finfluence, the officer brought the car
OL,17,Fto a stop on Barnsley Road.
