OL,3,CMan caught drink driving with child in
OL,4,Cthe car in Barnsley appears at court
OL,6,FAs they opened the door, the driver
OL,7,FDavid Martin, aged 28, from Thurnscoe
OL,8,Fwas seen trying to hide a can of beer
OL,9,Fthat was in the car with him.
OL,11,FMartin also had a child in the car
OL,12,Fwith him.
OL,14,FThe officer breathalysed Martin, who
OL,15,Fblew 68, with the legal limit being 35.
