OL,3,CMan caught drink driving with child in
OL,4,Cthe car in Barnsley appears at court
OL,6,FRoads Policing Sergeant Brandon Brown
OL,7,Fsaid: "Drink driving is a reckless and
OL,8,Fdangerous act that puts innocent lives
OL,9,Fat risk, and what was made worse by
OL,10,Fthis incident, is that Martin decided
OL,11,Fto risk an innocent child's life in
OL,12,Fhis care.
OL,14,F"Anyone who chooses to get behind the
OL,15,Fwheel while impaired is selfish, and
OL,16,Fyour actions will not be tolerated. We
OL,17,Fremain committed to taking action to
OL,18,Fkeep our roads and communities safe."
