OL,6,FYou are six times more likely to be
OL,7,Finvolved in a fatal collision if you
OL,8,Fdrive while under the influence of
OL,9,Falcohol. You can lose your life, end
OL,10,Fup in prison, lose your licence,
OL,11,Ffamily and job. It's not worth the
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,FMartin appeared before Barnsley
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on 22 December and
OL,16,Fwas disqualified from driving for 15
OL,17,Fmonths, and ordered to attend
OL,18,Frehabilitation activity for 10 days.
